description:
Add real integration tests for multi-step tool calling without mocking streamTextIterator.

## Test Scenarios
- Single tool call followed by text response
- Multiple sequential tool call rounds
- Tool call that triggers another tool call
- maxSteps limiting iterations
- stopWhen/stopConditions evaluation

## Pattern
```typescript
let responseCount = 0;
const model = new MockLanguageModelV3({
  doStream: async () => {
    switch (responseCount++) {
      case 0: return { stream: /* tool call */ };
      case 1: return { stream: /* final text */ };
    }
  },
});
```

## Acceptance Criteria
- [ ] Tests run without mocking streamTextIterator
- [ ] Multi-step iteration is verified end-to-end
- [ ] Step count and stop conditions are tested
